            <title type="main">
              <hi rend="i">BLAKE IN BUFFALO</hi>
            </title>
          </head>
          <p>The Albright-Knox Art Gallery in Buffalo, New York, mounted a small exhibition of fourteen of
Blake’s engravings from Job and Dante series. These engravings were acquired by Albright-Knox in 1943. 
<hi rend="i">The Engraved Illustrations of William Blake</hi> was exhibited from 26 September 1986 to 25 January
1987.</p>
